To run Mibench on simplescalar
1. Edit Makefile in each benchmark program
change compiler from "gcc" to "/home/username/simplescalar/sslittle-na-sstrix/bin/gcc".

change any "ar" (if exists) to "home/username/simplescalar/sslittle-na-sstrix/bin/ar", same for "ranlib".

2. Run "make"

3. edit runme_large.sh/runme_small.sh

use /home/sechw/simplescalar/simplesim-3.0/sim-outorder or sim-safe to run

4. Run "bash runme_large.sh/runme_small.sh" 
